Class Clock

  • java.lang.Object
    • teetime.framework.AbstractStage
      • teetime.framework.AbstractProducerStage<Long>
        • teetime.stage.Clock

  • public class Clock
extends AbstractProducerStage<Long>
    This stage sends the current timestamp repeatedly with a given interval delay of intervalDelayInMs.
    Author:
    Nelson Tavares de Sousa
    Stage output:
    Current timestamp as long.
    Stage sketch:
     +------------------------+
 |                        |
 |                      +---+
 |      *INTERVAL* +--> |   |
 |                      +---+
 |                        |
 +------------------------+
